TextBlock.TextLine: The Deposition of Mary fuller sen'or Aged About 41 years
Saieth About the 23 or fouorth of
cam to our house and Charged me with
hur About my Daughter and Mary Thorne
she S'd Rachell was drawing: my Brother Joseph
Fuller's boy Com in and said their Betty was fall
and this was as shee S'd Rechell pased by: hur: A comming to our house
and further Run up to my Brothers Joseph Fullers
Speke shee s'd The wommon with A whit Cape
